Definition: a movement in Europe from about 1650 until 1800 that advocated the use of reason and individualism instead of tradition and established doctrine
Example: the Enlightenment brought about many humanitarian reforms
Synonyms: Age_of_Reason, reform_movement, noun, time, historic_period, i, a, movement, in, Europe, from, about, until, that, advocated, the, use, of, reason, and, individualism, instead, tradition, established, doctrine, brought, many, humanitarian, reforms
Category: noun.group
